OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FA County Armagh man whose three
OL,8,Fbrothers were murdered by Loyalist
OL,9,Fgunmen fifty years ago has received an
OL,10,Fapology and been awarded #400,000 in
OL,11,Fdamages.
OL,13,FThe three victims were shot after
OL,14,Fgunmen entered the family's home in
OL,15,FWhitecross in January 1976.
OL,17,FEugene Reavey took a civil case
OL,18,Fagainst the PSNI and Ministry of
OL,19,FDefence (MOD) over claims that serving
OL,20,FUDR soldiers and an RUC officer joined
OL,21,Fthe plot to kill them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
