FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FJohn Martin, Brian and Anthony Reavey
OL,8,Fwere shot dead at their family home in
OL,9,FWhitecross back in January 1976.
OL,11,FIn court on Thursday, it was announced
OL,12,Fthat the PSNI has agreed to pay their
OL,13,Fbrother #175,000, while the MoD will
OL,14,Fpay him #225,000, to settle both
OL,15,Factions.
OL,17,FAn apology was also read out on behalf
OL,18,Fof Chief Constable Jon Boutcher for
OL,19,Finadequacies in the investigation of
OL,20,Fthe murders.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
