FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FIt stated: "The Chief Constable
OL,8,Facknowledges and accepts that the
OL,9,Fbehaviour and failures of members of
OL,10,Fthe RUC may have contributed to the
OL,11,Fmurders of John Martin Reavey, Brian
OL,12,FReavey and Anthony Reavey and to the
OL,13,Floss suffered by the Plaintiff and his
OL,14,Ffamily."
OL,16,FLoyalist paramilitary gunmen entered
OL,17,Fthe cottage and shot the three victims
OL,18,Fwhile they were watching TV.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
