PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FJohn Martin, 25, and Brian, 22, were
OL,8,Fboth killed instantly, while 17-year-
OL,9,Fold Anthony died in hospital later
OL,10,Fthat month.
OL,12,FThe shootings were carried out using a
OL,13,Fmachine gun taken from a British army
OL,14,Fbase at Glenanne, Co Armagh by a rogue
OL,15,FUDR corporal in an "inside job" which
OL,16,Fhad deadly consequences, it was
OL,17,Fclaimed.
OL,26,@wD@TOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
