PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FMr Reavey sought damages for
OL,8,Fnegligence, misfeasance in public
OL,9,Foffice and the trauma from his alleged
OL,10,Ftreatment in the aftermath of the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FThe murders took place in the same
OL,14,Fmonth as 10 Protestant workmen were
OL,15,Fstopped in a van and shot dead at
OL,16,FKingsmills, Co Armagh.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
