PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FPart of the case also involved claims
OL,8,Fthat RUC officers also began to harass
OL,9,Fhim following the murders, stopping
OL,10,Fhis car and detaining him for hours at
OL,11,Fa time.
OL,13,FMr Reavey said he suffered bouts of
OL,14,Fdisturbed sleep and nightmares about
OL,15,Fthe gun attack in the family's cottage.
OL,17,FOn day five of the case it was
OL,18,Fdisclosed that negotiations had led to
OL,19,Fsettlements being reached with both
OL,20,Fthe PSNI and the MoD.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
