PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781888761
OL,3,CApology and damages for Eugene Reavey
OL,4,Cwhose brothers were murdered 50 years
OL,5,Cago
OL,7,FPolice also accept without reservation
OL,8,Fthat Mr Reavey and his three murdered
OL,9,Fbrothers had no involvement whatsoever
OL,10,Fin any paramilitary or terrorist
OL,11,Factivity, the court was told.
OL,13,FWith the behaviour of some RUC members
OL,14,Faccepted to have potentially
OL,15,Fcontributed to the killings, Mr Fahy
OL,16,Fadded: "The Chief Constable apologises
OL,17,Funreservedly for any such behaviour
OL,18,Fand failures and for the enduring
OL,19,Fconsequences that have flowed from
OL,20,Fthem."
OL,26,@xD@HOU|D@FO]
